column16: Freddie Freeman singles on a line drive to left fielder Kevin Pillar.   Nick Markakis to 2nd.

Bobby Wilson singles on a line drive to center fielder Dalton Pompey.   Steven Souza Jr.   scores.    Allan Dykstra to 2nd.
Asdrubal Cabrera grounds out, shortstop Steve Tolleson to first baseman Justin Smoak.   Brandon Guyer scores.
Asdrubal Cabrera grounds out, third baseman Josh Donaldson to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.

Chris Davis grounds out, second baseman Devon Travis to first baseman Justin Smoak.
Colt Hynes intentionally walks Steve Pearce.
Alejandro De Aza strikes out swinging.
